  "modName": "SM Drop Lit Torches",
  "summary": "This mod allows you to drop lit torches to the ground when you can&#39;t spare a hand to hold it.",
  "descriptionHtml": "Awards and Features\r<br />----------------------------------\r<br />[center][url=http://www.skyrimgems.com][img]http://i.imgur.com/hXQSy.png[/img][/url][/center]\r<br />\r<br />This mod allows you to drop lit torches to the ground when you can&#39;t spare a hand to hold it.\r<br />\r<br />When you switch from a torch to another weapon/spell/shield the previously equipped torch will be dropped to the floor.\r<br />\r<br />If you pick up the torch on the ground without a weapon in your left hand or with no weapons drawn and you are not sneaking you will automatically re-equip the torch.\r<br />\r<br />You can also manually drop a torch from your inventory and you will drop a lit torch (this only works when dropping a single torch)\r<br />\r<br />When you pick up a torch for the first time a new lesser power called Hotkey Torch will be added. \r<br />\r<br />When you equip this power the following will occur:\r<br />- If you have a weapon in your left hand and you are in combat you will drop a torch to the ground.\r<br />- If you already have a torch equipped it will re-equip your previous item in your left hand (dropping the torch if nessecary)\r<br />- Otherwise you will just equip a torch.\r<br />\r<br />You can also use the hotkey torch in the favourites menu. This is better than favouriting a torch because it will not be removed when you run out of torches.\r<br />\r<br />Prerequisites\r<br />----------------------------------------------\r<br />SKSE must be installed http://skse.silverlock.org\r<br />\r<br />Notes\r<br />----------------------------------------------\r<br />-This mod should work on all carriable light sources or mods that add new torches etc.\r<br />\r<br />Uninstall\r<br />----------------------------------------------\r<br />To cleanly uninstall the mod, in game enter into the skyrim console\r<br />\r<br />set DropLitTorchUninstall to 1\r<br />\r<br />And wait for the confirmation message before saving and disabling the mod\r<br />\r<br />\r<br />Version History\r<br />----------------------------------------------\r<br />v3.0\r<br />- SKSE is now required as it fixes all the bugs with torches not dropping for certain equipment types.\r<br />- Fixed issue where right handed weapons caused torches to drop in certain situations.\r<br />- Added cleaner uninstall option\r<br />- You no longer need weapons drawn when switching to a weapon to drop a torch. The check for weapons drawn was unreliable in certain animation events.\r<br />- Hotkey torch behavior changed:\r<br />\t*If you have a weapon in your left hand and you are in combat you will drop a torch to the ground.\r<br />\t*If you already have a torch equipped it will re-equip your previous item in your left hand (dropping the torch if nessecary)\r<br />\t*Otherwise you will just equip a torch.\r<br />- If you are sneaking when you pick up a torch on the ground you will not auto equip it.",
